Interface Subscribable<T>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Multi<T>, Single<T>
    public interface Subscribable<T>
extends Flow.Publisher<T>
    Decorated publisher that allows subscribing to individual events with java functions.
